Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成員確實有6人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顧問呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長接受申請了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵咪部成了結女的正式社團了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡動物的愛理竟然也加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底用了什麼魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過猜的話我倒是能猜到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:00:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
